message: I've added a few links. The reason why I've changed ''Iran'' to ''Persia'' is because Iran was known as Persia in the west pre 1935. It makes absolutely no sense to call Qajar, Afsharid and Safavid Persia ''Iran'' this is the English Wikipedia and it was known as Persia in English back then.
